{"tid":592714,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實講真 入到asso hd 已經好勁","createTime":"2018-03-14T12:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T12:59:14.000Z","uid":68626,"like":16,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e01bc738d7c7eb1cd308b52176d5e0c1fe92b7","tid":592714,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:17:51.000Z","msg":"多數話asso hd唔勁個D<br />\n都係無asso hd既人<br />\n一味就係到話咩入唔到大學正垃圾<br />\n中學同asso學習模式唔同，同一個人已經可以係gpa3.8同22222既分別<br />\n依加統計數據 入到大學係頭20%左右<br />\n換番做錢計 基本上asso hd =香港既中產級數 應該坐底有三四百萬<br />\n去到found dip左右既人思想已經好成熟<br />\n唔係話實力高過對手就一定高分(自問5**實力 間唔中做pastapaper都會覺得其實幾難)<br />\n可以話非常接近大學生<br />\n去到asso gpa 2.5同3.8既能力差距其實係好少好少好少 基本上55波<br />\n可能3.8既心情差少少已經c左<br />\n講真連登我諗入面有大學學歷既百份比連10%都唔知有冇<br />\nasso hd咁都唔叫勁 我真係唔知咩叫勁 唔通下下要上到劍橋哈佛叫勁?"},{"pid":"02984e73359b19c7623a80902c0719fbb47b30bc","tid":592714,"uid":152520,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"今次勉強咗啲"},{"pid":"542a1a5cb434e75e435b8ba6f50514f4186ca1df","tid":592714,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02984e73359b19c7623a80902c0719fbb47b30bc","tid":592714,"uid":152520,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"今次勉強咗啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:21:11.000Z","msg":"以事論事"},{"pid":"1345968230de37069570fab216e622f2fe424d40","tid":592714,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"83c5882eccea920890978cd4b7befc912a51f194","tid":592714,"uid":32380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"3.8上到大學<br />\n2.5上唔到<br />\n差少少？"},{"pid":"00c6c862fd89350c7bb72817ec2b25732408a733","tid":592714,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"me totally agger with u"},{"pid":"4c934775956e300828e7707ea27daebd48c5d2f1","tid":592714,"uid":137166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor